{"tid":1877834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】七旬伯伯唔夠快排逾十次皆撲空　市民呻買廁紙口罩難","createTime":"2020-02-13T08:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T09:41:50.000Z","uid":85180,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8860ef5f355e583baa5ee459c485d779fb7d8ff4","tid":1877834,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】七旬伯伯唔夠快排逾十次皆撲空 市民呻買廁紙口罩難<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3997669/org/7f0faf98b4f0703bc8af9337130b76f5.jpg/u8gqZ82iLew79ecIkJLVOu1oyuaP8Q6AdMcQZXTHEGU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3997669%2Forg%2F7f0faf98b4f0703bc8af9337130b76f5.jpg%2Fu8gqZ82iLew79ecIkJLVOu1oyuaP8Q6AdMcQZXTHEGU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=3eb0fe80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情肆虐，市面上的口罩搶購潮不斷。日本城今早（13日）再於facebook宣布，於指定四間分店出售口罩，每人限購一盒，結果有人歡喜有人愁，仍然有多人撲空。有 七旬伯伯表示，已試過排十幾次，但每次都失敗而回；亦有市民無奈道：「廁紙又買唔到，米又買唔到，口罩又買唔到！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3997654/org/0dadb805c9c1bd88cac84334fe646dfe.jpg/hgcK6_nAxFuQBblcLFJ5UolDUsC49zViGL2fFDK9nxQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3997654%2Forg%2F0dadb805c9c1bd88cac84334fe646dfe.jpg%2FhgcK6_nAxFuQBblcLFJ5UolDUsC49zViGL2fFDK9nxQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=bfe1ab40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者一早到位於荔枝角的日本城視察，雖然口罩只有360盒，但已有逾500人於商場輪候，人龍打了多個「蛇餅」，一度需要保安員在場維持秩序。現場職員不足30分鐘便派完所有籌號，由於口罩仍在運送過程，遂通知成功取籌人士稍後再取。<br />\n<br />\n七旬伯伯望政府限制口罩供應<br />\n<br />\n77歲的蘇伯伯來到店外始發覺撲空，他稱已排隊十幾次，但都未有成功。他說：「每次聽到消息就去買，萬寧又去過、屈臣氏又去過、吉之島又去過......」每次都因不夠快，只可失望而回。他指，家中只剩下數個口罩，只好減少外出次數，又說：「一買餸就買一個禮拜。」他稱到用盡口罩時，只可用衣服掩著臉去買餸。他慨嘆市面上藥房的口罩昂貴，見過100元只得3個，根本無法應付。他期望政府限制口罩供應售予市民，又說：「唔貪心要佢派，但依家買都冇得買！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3997649/org/50614fc2a51060c850d1fa13d16f96bf.jpg/CSkpNJa-WraNFFOt5jFMb3tdHRHx8lMx3BwqPfYcKj0?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3997649%2Forg%2F50614fc2a51060c850d1fa13d16f96bf.jpg%2FCSkpNJa-WraNFFOt5jFMb3tdHRHx8lMx3BwqPfYcKj0%3Fv%3Dw640&h=15d39124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3997646/org/fc65f592e07a6b57fb3d393baf66962e.jpg/8OObWv1CA1HLgUUAdvfvcMb1JNVhX7N8DZwPKyecDys?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3997646%2Forg%2Ffc65f592e07a6b57fb3d393baf66962e.jpg%2F8OObWv1CA1HLgUUAdvfvcMb1JNVhX7N8DZwPKyecDys%3Fv%3Dw640&h=8a5af075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3997645/org/97e74ecc58427dad16793d784f52a552.jpg/keoyRNTPCPXqFfZTcEcSdrbEuPgFGa5DKdsz_wPbM_8?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3997645%2Forg%2F97e74ecc58427dad16793d784f52a552.jpg%2FkeoyRNTPCPXqFfZTcEcSdrbEuPgFGa5DKdsz_wPbM_8%3Fv%3Dw640&h=cb19474d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3997647/org/7af513782640704f4d7da68f4ba36917.jpg/DnrD3t-L9TIJ09JNTjfMx3u_NDMCpo0Sj4QcaaWEHGk?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3997647%2Forg%2F7af513782640704f4d7da68f4ba36917.jpg%2FDnrD3t-L9TIJ09JNTjfMx3u_NDMCpo0Sj4QcaaWEHGk%3Fv%3Dw640&h=db3b3948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民嘆上班無暇買日用品<br />\n<br />\n亦有落空的市民大表無奈，她稱原本打算去附近的超市買廁紙，但未有買到，見多人在輪口罩亦排一排，結果兩邊皆落空。她大呼好辛苦：「廁紙又買唔到，米又買唔到，口罩又買唔到......」又直言平日要上班，根本無空買日常用品。她透露，家中只剩下十多個口罩，直言：「都冇得點算！」<br />\n<br />\n今日放假的黄先生表示，成功第一次排隊買到口罩，並說：「終於排到第一盒！」自言覺得幸運。他又說，因工種所限，不能夠在家工作，家中只剩下二十多個口罩要兩人使用。被問及會否擔心口罩不足，他苦笑：「一定唔夠。」但他稱不太擔心，相信未來陸續返貨，又批評政府防疫措施「唔掂」，與澳門政府相差極遠，直言：「又唔封關，封啲唔封啲。」"},{"pid":"151604bffc5aac119cce57a8e6a6fa5448a0bbc5","tid":1877834,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"【誅連九族】請立即將少數派同張曉明綑綁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1877679/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1877679/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4ec0d8541af359cf6b95ed25587e6721843579a5","tid":1877834,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:50:54.000Z","msg":"D柒頭搶撚夠廁紙未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81c7a2289793faf21ac734637cd3d41bec5e07d","tid":1877834,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"排十幾次仲哂左十幾個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09e1577b13b9e88b8a790795d8eda5aef8675b6","tid":1877834,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f81c7a2289793faf21ac734637cd3d41bec5e07d","tid":1877834,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"排十幾次仲哂左十幾個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"最撚勁係香港人仲未出黎反抗"},{"pid":"fbb605ca7b305c884abe8473736b252daa56f679","tid":1877834,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"話就話存貨充足，事實上廁紙同米個貨架係長期無貨賣"},{"pid":"ad57abb80dd98eb169d1575a6baa3f2ac941827f","tid":1877834,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb605ca7b305c884abe8473736b252daa56f679","tid":1877834,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"話就話存貨充足，事實上廁紙同米個貨架係長期無貨賣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:58:48.000Z","msg":"同之前口罩一樣"},{"pid":"91dec43013ed907b7cd8556b78de1f55b3b90b31","tid":1877834,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d09e1577b13b9e88b8a790795d8eda5aef8675b6","tid":1877834,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f81c7a2289793faf21ac734637cd3d41bec5e07d","tid":1877834,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"排十幾次仲哂左十幾個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"最撚勁係香港人仲未出黎反抗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:00:32.000Z","msg":"返工好緊要"},{"pid":"9bab5a1da19d00dafa5784c8fd65f6001533bfa4","tid":1877834,"uid":146673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"其實我地班私人公司打工仔夠慘啦, <br />\n又無得home office, <br />\n日日至少都要用一個口罩, <br />\n公司又唔會提供, 一係就俾d 黑心口罩你都唔會敢帶同拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算有呢d 排隊, 我地要番工又可以排隊咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁迫於無奈咪又係要食炒價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班廢老排一排隊又晒一個口罩, <br />\n佢地可以留喺又唔留, <br />\n根本就有好多成班帶住口罩出去飲早茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fd92bb4d786d9420ea9092ca304c18ecec7723","tid":1877834,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:41:50.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}